data.description: Location, location, location!! This house is a short walk or golf cart ride to all of the Glenloch area amenities. This home boasts 5 bedrooms (3 up, 2 down) and 2.5 baths. Enter into the home's spacious living room and just of the living room you will enjoy the kitchen with ample cabinets. The kitchen allows access to the raised back deck where you can enjoy indoor/ outdoor entertaining in your privately fenced backyard. Additionally, this home features an outdoor storage building. Come and see this house for yourself!
